  <channel>
    <title>Water contributor: Cannon Michael</title>
    <description>Cannon Michael is a sixth-generation California farmer and president of his family’s farm, Bowles Farming Company. The farm uses organic and conventional practices to grow tomatoes and other food and fiber crops primarily on drip irrigation powered by solar energy. Cannon lives on the farm with his wife and three sons. He is active in local and state water leadership and education. He serves on the board of the Water Education Foundation.
</description>
